Title: When creating a folder, it is no longer necessary to specify a name
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: rest-api
Date: 1683190474
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.1.0p28

The folder creation endpoint no longer requires a name, only a title. If no name
is given, the title will be used as a basis to generate one. Note that you can create
as many folders with the same title in the same directory as you want.
This matches the behaviour of the GUI.

